# Product: Forger 

## Functions 
World & Agent Genesis
 — AI generates world base, agent personalities, and initial scripts, adapting to user input for maximal personalization using a multi-step conversational tool.

Agent Interaction
 — Simulate interactions between agents within a created world, generating dialogues and environment responses.

Human Agent Roleplay — Allows users to step into the world as a 'human agent' (NPC), directly interacting with AI agents and the environment.

Live-World Encounters — A live environment where user's agents can interact and converse with agents from other users, with logged chat histories for review.

Personalized Question Flow
 — Implement a multi-step, conversational onboarding where subsequent questions are dynamically generated based on user responses using a tool.

World Template Selection — Offer diverse world templates with a few initial questions to tailor world and agent generation to user preferences.

## Design
Character.ai - World templates (page2)
Latitude - Cool - target tech-savvy people
Dynamic - Minimize boredom
Brand color - Orange x Blue
